# BD68 Dev v1.0 Loader For OpenCode

Load `@bd68-dev-v1-0/BD68_PROFILE.md` at the start of the session.

Before using a bundled reference, open `@bd68-dev-v1-0/references/SOURCE_INDEX.md`.
Treat the files in `@bd68-dev-v1-0/references/` as curated GitHub-backed local retrieval sources, not as optional notes.

Use these references only when needed:
- `@bd68-dev-v1-0/references/impeccable.md` before frontend brainstorming or design planning.
- `@bd68-dev-v1-0/references/concise-planning.md` before writing a plan, roadmap, or task breakdown.
- `@bd68-dev-v1-0/references/antigravity.md` only when the current tool or skill stack is insufficient and a repeated need exists.

Treat `Shubhamsaboo/awesome-llm-apps` as an idea catalog only, not as a technical baseline or source of truth.
Before implementation, confirm API and SDK behavior with official docs.

Treat the BD68 profile as the default operating model for BD68 and WildSoul work in this environment.
